Build a web page using Bootstrap's container and card components to showcase product information. Apply custom CSS properties to style the cards with a unique background color, adjust the text color, and add padding to the content area. Additionally, ensure that the cards have a slight shadow to create a subtle visual effect.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Styled Cards with Bootstrap</title>
    <!-- Include Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <!-- Include custom CSS styles -->
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        
        .custom-card {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        h4 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card custom-card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title">Item 1</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">High-quality and innovative.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card custom-card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title">Item 2</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">Elegance and functionality combined.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card custom-card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title">Item 3</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">The ultimate solution for your needs.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Include Bootstrap JS and Popper.js -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
